ve.org/web/20191115162618/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478240-20190901.htm?spTabChangeable=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=scmp3025294>{{cite news|title=Hong Kong protests: class boycott hits schools on first day of term|date=2019-09-02|work=|publisher=[[南華早報|南華早報]]|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education/article/3025294/hong-kong-protests-thousands-school-students-expected-join|accessdate=2019-11-16|archive-date=2019-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115170323/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education/article/3025294/hong-kong-protests-thousands-school-students-expected-join|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動|反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動]]期間<ref name=apple20200127>{{cite news|title=籲政府還年輕人希望 陳狄安校長:不要怪責教育|work=[[李家文|李家文]]|date=2020-01-27|publisher=[[壹週刊_(香港)|壹週刊]]|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VUuBlvFU2GQ|access-date=2021-06-22|archive-date=2021-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624222310/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VUuBlvFU2GQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，該校於11月發布通告宣布復課。通告提到[[遊戲|遊戲]]和[[社交網絡|社交網絡]]平台最近被用來引誘、施壓和恐嚇學生參與示威以換取報酬。該校接到[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]的詢問，稱上述消息是[[教育局_(香港)|教育局]]工作人員通報的，工作人員建議該校提醒家長。因為教育局是官方機構，校長信任他們，所以沒有質疑信息的真實性。<ref name=apple20191122>{{cite news|title=【抗暴之戰】疑引用網上截圖 教育局職員致電籲校長提醒學生勿「收錢示威」|date=2019-11-22|publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]|url=https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191122/TQ772XCZVNIJMNPHI27AY3D2TU|access-date=2021-06-22|archive-date=2021-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210622204229/https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191122/TQ772XCZVNIJMNPHI27AY3D2TU/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年，隨著[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]爆發，課程被暫停，學生只能在家中學習。在整個停課期間，所有科目都進行了在線學習，「停課不停學」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=HKU collaborates with edX to offer free HKU MOOC certification to secondary school students in Hong Kong|url=https://indiaeducationdiary.in/hku-collaborates-with-edx-to-offer-free-hku-mooc-certification-to-secondary-school-students-in-hong-kong|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=indiaeducationdiary.in|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219140522/https://indiaeducationdiary.in/hku-collaborates-with-edx-to-offer-free-hku-mooc-certification-to-secondary-school-students-in-hong-kong/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在停課期間，該校[[科學教育|科學部]]製作了影片，解釋了[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]的詳細情況。<ref name=covidsci>{{Cite web|title=COVID 19 Video Science Department|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=13zEL6yZGg0&feature=youtu.be&fbclid=IwAR1DpmF-3fqI5SdXwtYPljePS61xdSmEwEG3Dk0eWXie8YTcMWxi4eni35k|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=港青基信書院}}</ref>這疫情妨礙了家長的生計，學校就凍結了下一學年的學費。<ref name=mp1586371470839>{{cite news|title=疫情礙家長生計 直資國際校紛助紓困 男拔港青基信凍學費|date=2020-04-09|work=|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20200409/s00001/1586371470839/疫情礙家長生計-直資國際校紛助紓困-男拔港青基信凍學費|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716211831/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200409/s00001/1586371470839/%e7%96%ab%e6%83%85%e7%a4%99%e5%ae%b6%e9%95%b7%e7%94%9f%e8%a8%88-%e7%9b%b4%e8%b3%87%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e6%a0%a1%e7%b4%9b%e5%8a%a9%e7%b4%93%e5%9b%b0-%e7%94%b7%e6%8b%94%e6%b8%af%e9%9d%92%e5%9f%ba%e4%bf%a1%e5%87%8d%e5%ad%b8%e8%b2%bb|dead-url=no}}</ref>學校已向[[旅行社|旅行社]]支付或承諾支付超過700,000港元的訂金，用於組織遊學團，而今年遊學團已全部取消。當政府決定向所有海外國家發布紅色旅遊警告時，旅行社和航空公司主動與學校聯繫，討論補償安排。<ref name=rthk20200317>{{cite news|title=保險業聯會：紅色警示或可取回一半未能索取款項|date=2020-03-17|work=|publisher=[[香港電台|香港電台]]|url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515104-20200317.htm|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405074343/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515104-20200317.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>IGCSE和GCE考試被取消，儘管該校聲稱不太擔心對學生升學的影響，因為當時大多數學生已經獲得了有條件的錄取通知。<ref name=mp1585160890419>{{cite news|title=GCE考試取消 學校：不太擔心影響升學|date=2020-03-26|work=|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20200326/s00001/1585160890419/gce考試取消-學校-不太擔心影響升學|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717190849/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200326/s00001/1585160890419/gce%e8%80%83%e8%a9%a6%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88-%e5%ad%b8%e6%a0%a1-%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%aa%e6%93%94%e5%bf%83%e5%bd%b1%e9%9f%bf%e5%8d%87%e5%ad%b8|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於[[2019冠狀病毒病香港疫情|2019冠狀病毒病香港疫情]]有所下降，學校在2021年2月安排老師接受[[2019冠狀病毒病檢測|2019冠狀病毒病檢測]]，並改變整個學校的課程，讓學生在[[新春|新春]]後重返學校恢復上課。校長告訴全體老師為測試做好心理準備。<ref>{{Cite web|title=教育局公布農曆年假後可三分一學生回校 教職員每兩周檢測一次|url=https://www.hk01.com/親子/583058/教育局公布農曆年假後可三分一學生回校-教職員每兩周檢測一次|access-date=2021-05-05|date=2021-02-03|last=李紫銘|work=[[香港01|香港01]]|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2021-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727095025/https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/583058/%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E5%B9%B4%E5%81%87%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%9B%9E%E6%A0%A1-%E6%95%99%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%AF%8F%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=apple20210212>{{cite news|title=兩校擬安排教員強檢換全校復課 校方稱學生利益為先 老師轟「道德綁架」|date=2021-02-12|publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]|url=https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210212/ODR5RWYBJNFU3IQN2SBOT2SSM4|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212001817/https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210212/ODR5RWYBJNFU3IQN2SBOT2SSM4/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=教員檢測可申全校復課 有幼稚園擬下月1日恢復面授|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210217/bkn-20210217101744821-0217_00822_001.html|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=[[東方日報_(香港)|on.cc東網]]|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2021-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219003013/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210217/bkn-20210217101744821-0217_00822_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年2月8日，[[陳狄安|陳狄安]]校長宣布他將在本學年結束時轉到[[英華書院|英華書院]]。盧裕敏副校長將擔任校長一職。<ref>{{Cite web|title=英華書院校長鄭鈞傑8月辭任 港青基信書院校長陳狄安接任|url=https://www.hk01.com/親子/601405/英華書院校長鄭鈞傑8月辭任-港青基信書院校長陳狄安接任|accessdate=2021-03-23|date=2021-03-19|last=王淑君|work=[[香港01|香港01]]|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2021-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210717041656/https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/601405/%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%84%AD%E9%88%9E%E5%82%918%E6%9C%88%E8%BE%AD%E4%BB%BB-%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E5%9F%BA%E4%BF%A1%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%99%B3%E7%8B%84%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-03-19|title=直資議會主席陳狄安獲任英華書院新校長 9月1日起生效|url=https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1526290/即時-港聞-直資議會主席陳狄安獲任英華書院新校長-9月1日起生效|website=[[星島日報|星島日報]]|accessdate=2021-03-21|archive-date=2021-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210622204406/https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1526290/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%9B%B4%E8%B3%87%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%99%B3%E7%8B%84%E5%AE%89%E7%8D%B2%E4%BB%BB%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B0%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7-9%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-03-19|title=英華書院校長鄭鈞傑8月離任　由港青基信書院校長陳狄安接任|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210319/bkn-20210319140542412-0319_00822_001.html|website=[[東方日報_(香港)|東方日報]]|accessdate=2021-03-21|archive-date=2021-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210622204323/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210319/bkn-20210319140542412-0319_00822_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-03-19|title=直資學校議會主席陳狄安9月接任英華書院校長|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20210319/s00001/1616137697350/直資學校議會主席陳狄安9月接任英華書院校長|website=[[明報|明報]]|accessdate=2021-03-21|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418050544/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210319/s00001/1616137697350/%E7%9B%B4%E8%B3%87%E5%AD%