服務團隊包括[[到燴|餐飲服務組]]<ref name=st20101216 />、[[傳福音|基督徒團契]]<ref name=mp20120724 />、[[義工|社會服務團]]、[[香港青年獎勵計劃|香港青年獎勵計劃]]、[[環境友善|環保學會]]、[[童軍活動|童軍]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=香港童軍總會新界地域|url=https://www.scout-ntr.org.hk/mainweb/big5/district/groups.php?dcode=lid|accessdate=2022-01-31|work=|publisher=[[香港童軍總會|香港童軍總會]]|archive-date=2022-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131121720/https://www.scout-ntr.org.hk/mainweb/big5/district/groups.php?dcode=lid|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=香港童軍總會大嶼山區|url=https://www.facebook.com/lantauscouts|accessdate=2022-01-31|work=|publisher=[[香港童軍總會|香港童軍總會]]}}</ref>、舞台管理團隊<ref name=scmp20110413 /><ref name=standard20110420 />和[[圖書館員|圖書館員]]等。<ref name=2019_Yearbook /><ref name=a_MainBooklet_2019_final />

===出色的運動表現===
該校每兩年在[[青衣運動場|青衣運動場]]舉行陸運會<ref name=mp1449478762415 /><ref name=scmp101058 />，並每年在[[東涌游泳池|東涌游泳池]]舉行水運會。<ref name=swim>{{Cite web|title=Annual Swimming Gala|url=https://yhkcc.edu.hk/en/news_details.php?wid=97&sid=%20&id=595&cid=9&page=7|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=港青基信書院|archive-date=2022-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220201072428/https://yhkcc.edu.hk/en/news_details.php?wid=97&sid=%20&id=595&cid=9&page=7|dead-url=no}}</ref>

運動隊在大多數校際比賽中表現良好。<ref name=ladder />他們包括[[田徑|田徑]]<ref name=athletics2019>{{Cite web|title=HKSSF Inter-school Athletics Championships|url=https://yhkcc.edu.hk/en/album_details.php?wid=107&sid=&id=51&cid=1&page=3|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=港青基信書院|archive-date=2020-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121211254/http://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/en/news_events/latest_news/index.php?id=1362|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[羽毛球|羽毛球]]<ref name=badminton2019>{{Cite web|title=HKSSF Inter-school Badminton Competition|url=https://yhkcc.edu.hk/en/album_details.php?wid=107&sid=&id=253&cid=1&page=14|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=港青基信書院|archive-date=2022-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131172939/https://yhkcc.edu.hk/en/album_details.php?wid=107&sid=&id=253&cid=1&page=14|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[籃球|籃球]]<ref name=st20180308>{{cite news|title=基信「世界軍」攻防互體諒|date=2018-03-08|work=|publisher=[[星島日報|星島日報]]|url=http://std.stheadline.com|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2020-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412160404/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/111/combined.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=oriental20180419>{{cite news|title=張振興求突破 基信省招牌|date=2018-04-19|work=|publisher=[[東方日報_(香港)|東方日報]]|url=https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/sport/20180419/00286_005.html|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2022-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220131172803/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/sport/20180419/00286_005.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=stand20181223>{{cite news|title=【學界籃球精英賽】裘錦秋錯失反超機會 基信險勝1分首名出線|date=2018-12-23|work=|publisher=[[立場新聞|立場新聞]]|url=https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/233822?fbclid=IwAR3PUkFyenv76QZShnmPp9NxFZWj0uuHV-ZAcqBtKiEZRk_Z9EUu90qwfeA|accessdate=2020-05-04}}</ref>、[[啦啦隊|啦啦隊]]<ref name=scmp20120402>{{cite news|title=Happenings school news: YHKCC|date=2012-04-02|work=|publisher=[[南華早報|南華早報]]|url=https://www.scmp.com|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2022-02-05|archive-url=https://web