===全方位學習營===
該校在每年秋天為初中生組織為期三日兩夜的全方位學習營（Life-Wide-Learning camp），以取代一日野餐作為他們的其他學習經歷。露營地點包括[[西貢半島|西貢半島]]等。<ref name=standard20111011>{{cite news|title=Life-wide Learning Camp of YHKCC|date=2011-10-11|work=|publisher=[[英文虎報|英文虎報]]|url=https://www.thestandard.com.hk|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2022-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220205094720/https://www.thestandard.com.hk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==公開活動==
自2012年開始，該校的學生和老師每年12月都舉辦「國際嘉年華」<ref name=10th />，這是繼2011年「家年華」<ref name=mp20111117>{{cite news|title=港青基信書院「家年華」吸引逾二千二百人入場|date=2011-11-17|work=|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|url=https://news.mingpao.com|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716191815/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/21/5_MP_17%20Nov%2011.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Isse 4 Dec 2011 - Jan 2012: YHKCC International Night 2011|url=https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/23/7_Our%20Tung%20Chung_Dec%2011%20Jan%2012%20Issue.pdf|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=Our Tung Chung|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718000309/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/23/7_Our%20Tung%20Chung_Dec%2011%20Jan%2012%20Issue.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>和「國際之夜」之後每年的公開活動。<ref name=st20110106 /><ref name=st20101216 /><ref name=standard20111220>{{cite news|title=Attention please, welcome to YHKCC Airlines|date=2011-12-20|work=|publisher=[[英文虎報|英文虎報]]|url=https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/attachment/news/newsDownload/1610681140yEsoi.pdf|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716183610/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/24/8_The%20Standard_20%20Dec%2011.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=mp20120111>{{cite news|title=港青基信書院「國際之夜」展開奇妙世界旅程|date=2012-01-11|work=|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|url=https://news.mingpao.com|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716181214/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/25/9_MP_11%20Jan%2012.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Isse 5 Feb - Mar 2012: YHKCC International Night 2011|url=https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/28/12_OTC_Issue%205_Feb-Mar%2012.pdf|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=Our Tung Chung|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716191828/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/28/12_OTC_Issue%205_Feb-Mar%2012.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>訪客可以在學校享受[[族群|民族美食]]<ref name=mp20160223>{{cite news|title=港青基信書院「國際嘉年華」|date=2016-02-23|work=|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|url=https://news.mingpao.com|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710113311/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/89/20150223_Ming%20Pao_IFF.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[巴剎|巴剎集市]]、遊戲<ref>{{Cite web|title=YHKCC International Fun Fair 2018|url=https://www.arounddb.com|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=AroundDB Magazine|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710112957/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/124/AroundDB_Jan_IFF%20post%20event.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>、充氣城堡和美術展覽。<ref>{{Cite web|title=YHKCC International Fun Fair|url=http://www.arounddb.com/events/yhkcc-international-fun-fair-2|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=AroundDB Magazine|archive-date=2020-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412160327/http://www.arounddb.com/events/yhkcc-international-fun-fair-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>訪客還可以在下午和晚上觀看才藝表演，<ref>{{Cite web|title=「奇蹟之書」異國冒險之旅|url=http://schoolike.hk/activity155.htm|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=|publisher=[[香港青年協會|香港青年協會]]|archive-date=2020-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412160312/http://schoolike.hk/activity155.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>展示世界各地不同國家的歌舞。<ref name=st20180114>{{cite news|title=港青基信書院 十五周年嘉年華|date=2018-01-14|work=|publisher=[[星島日報|星島日報]]|url=http://std.stheadline.com|accessdate=2020-05-04|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710113138/https://www.yhkcc.edu.hk/filemanager/ymcacc_newsclipping/en/upload/109/Sing%20Tao_20180114.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=standard20181217>{{cite news|title=A Roaring Success at the YHKCC International Fun Fair|date=2018-12-17|w